@startuml
title Weather Station State Transition Diagram

state Shutdown
state Running
state Configuration
state ControlledMode

[*] --> Shutdown : Initial state

Shutdown --> Running : power-up / restart

Running --> Configuration : changes or power-saving settings required
Running --> ControlledMode : remote control command
Running --> Shutdown : shutdown command

Configuration --> Running : configuration completed

Running --> Running : data collection triggered by clock
Running --> Running : summary preparation upon request
Running --> Running : status check upon request

ControlledMode --> Running : exit controlled mode
ControlledMode --> Shutdown : shutdown command

Shutdown --> [*] : terminate
@enduml
